---
title: Account Details
description: View your account details, log out, update your email address, or delete your account from here.
---

{% extends "layouts/default.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="cmp-container cmp-stack">
    <h1>
      Account Details
    </h1>
    <p data-logged-out hidden>
      You are not currently logged in. If you would like to log in or create an
      account, do so at the <a href="/login">Log In or Sign Up page</a>.
    </p>
    <p data-logged-in hidden>
      You are logged in as <span data-email-address></span>.
    </p>
    <div data-logged-in hidden>
      <button type="button" data-logout-button>
        Log Out
      </button>
    </div>
    <p data-logout-failure hidden>
      Oops! Something went wrong when logging you out. Reload and try again?
    </p>
    <div class="cmp-stack" data-logged-in hidden>
      <p>
        To change your email address, you'll need to have signed in recently.
        We'll send you a link that will take you to a page where you can change
        your email address.
      </p>
      <button type="button" data-update-email-button>
        Change Email Address
      </button>
      <p data-update-email-success hidden>
        Success! Check your email for a magic link (you may close this tab now).
      </p>
      <p data-update-email-failure hidden>
        Whoops! Something went wrong when trying to send your email. Try
        reloading the page and trying again.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="cmp-stack" data-logged-in hidden>
      <p>
        To delete your account, you'll need to have signed in recently. We'll
        send you a link that will take you to a page where you can delete your
        account.
      </p>
      <button type="button" data-delete-account-button>
        Delete Account
      </button>
      <p data-delete-account-success hidden>
        Success! Check your email for a magic link (you may close this tab now).
      </p>
      <p data-delete-account-failure hidden>
        Whoops! Something went wrong when trying to send your email. Try
        reloading the page and trying again.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}

{% block authScripts %}
  <script src="/assets/js/bundled/account.js" type="module"></script>
  <script src="/assets/js/legacy/account.js" nomodule></script>
{% endblock %}
